{"tid":2508044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BioNTech：以後每年或要再打武肺疫苗加強劑","createTime":"2021-04-28T12:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T13:45:20.000Z","uid":21470,"like":52,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"6ae4a40edee03771f762a0c5f679b840258f5160","tid":2508044,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:23:35.000Z","msg":"BioNTech：以後每年或要再打新冠疫苗加強劑<br />\n<br />\n德國藥廠BioNTech行政總裁薩欣預期，歐洲可以在8月前達致群體免疫，又說已接種新冠疫苗人士的數據顯示，BioNTech疫苗有效性會由原先的95%，跌至6個月後約91%，免疫反應減弱，因此需要注射第3針才能令疫苗保護再次恢復到近100％水平。現時普遍國家接種這款疫苗，第1、2針相隔3星期，他建議第3針應在第1針後9至12個月內注射，又預計以後可能每年或每18個月，要再打一針加強劑。<br />\n<br />\n對於有質疑指現時的疫苗，可能無法有效抵禦多款變種病毒，薩欣回應說，BioNTech已對30多種變種病毒作測試，包括英國流行的一款變種病毒，在實驗室中仍能產生良好中和反應，即使免疫反應變弱，仍然足夠，而對印度變種病毒的有效性就仍在研究，他充滿信心。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2389312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2389312&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzQKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=738592d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2389312</a>"},{"pid":"a6fc75f88f4c29595a2cb03841928e808a135979","tid":2508044,"uid":334957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c7b199ad1b4f4d448dde9400085b4b04238462","tid":2508044,"uid":263261,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:25:13.000Z","msg":"永續肺炎"},{"pid":"271e12140724fb50edbae3546c75e0f00d590edd","tid":2508044,"uid":40982,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:26:24.000Z","msg":"每年一次安樂死的機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1d48000a19625d248581e7e684de68eca4b705","tid":2508044,"uid":303599,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:26: